{"word":"Punishment","slug":"punishment","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Punishment</b> Death penalty:<br/> - Shall not be remitted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=35&verse=31'>Num 35:31</a> <br/> - In the Mosaic law the death penalty was inflicted for:<br/> b Murder<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=6'>Gen 9:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=35&verse=21'>Num 35:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=35&verse=33'>Num 35:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=6'>Deu 17:6</a><br/> b Adultery<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=10'>Lev 20:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=24'>Deu 22:24</a><br/> b Incest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=12'>Lev 20:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=14'>Lev 20:14</a><br/> b Bestiality<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=19'>Exo 22:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=16'>Lev 20:16</a><br/> b Sodomy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=18&verse=22'>Lev 18:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=13'>Lev 20:13</a><br/> b Incontinence<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=24'>Deu 22:24</a><br/> b Rape of a betrothed virgin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=22&verse=25'>Deu 22:25</a><br/> b Perjury<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=5&verse=4'>Zec 5:4</a><br/> b Kidnapping<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=16'>Exo 21:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=7'>Deu 24:7</a><br/> b Upon a priest's daughter, who committed fornication<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=21&verse=9'>Lev 21:9</a><br/> b Witchcraft<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=18'>Exo 22:18</a><br/> b Offering human sacrifice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=5'>Lev 20:5</a><br/> b Striking or cursing father or mother<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=15'>Exo 21:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=21&verse=17'>Exo 21:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=20&verse=9'>Lev 20:9</a><br/> b Disobedience to parents<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=21'>Deu 21:21</a><br/> b Theft<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=5&verse=4'>Zec 5:4</a><br/> b Blasphemy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=14'>Lev 24:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=16'>Lev 24:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=24&verse=23'>Lev 24:23</a><br/> b Sabbath desecration<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=35&verse=2'>Exo 35:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=15&verse=36'>Num 15:36</a><br/> b Prophesying falsely, or propagating false doctrines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=13&verse=10'>Deu 13:10</a><br/> b Sacrificing to false gods<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=20'>Exo 22:20</a><br/> b Refusing to abide by the decision of court<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=12'>Deu 17:12</a><br/> b Treason<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=2&verse=25'>1Ki 2:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=23'>Est 2:23</a><br/> b Sedition<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=37